#: ../../reference/translations.rst:2 3e883b5d419e4ba4bb0b46dbbf885702
msgid "Translations"
msgstr "翻译说明"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:4 f334cc8f92684385b171852d791f4eba
msgid ""
"This page documents how VoxCPM docs manage translations in the same "
"repository. The English pages under ``docs/`` remain the source of truth. "
"Chinese content is maintained through Sphinx gettext catalogs under "
"``docs/locale/zh_CN/LC_MESSAGES/``."
msgstr ""
"本页说明 VoxCPM 文档如何在同一仓库中管理翻译。``docs/`` 下的英文页面仍是权威来源；中文内容通过 Sphinx gettext 目录 "
"`` docs/locale/zh_CN/LC_MESSAGES/`` 维护。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:9 7fc032d8421b4fe1927086babc79b348
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:11 33144b551d8b4f02a5f1b116b602eb89
msgid "The translation workflow uses:"
msgstr "翻译工作流使用："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:13 6501e55888454b4b90f086e5cd8a1d2c
msgid "Sphinx gettext catalogs generated from the English source pages"
msgstr "由英文源页面生成的 Sphinx gettext 目录"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:14 80f7084c0ab04b3eacf6798c8d30d4e1
msgid "``sphinx-intl`` to create and update ``.po`` files"
msgstr "``sphinx-intl`` 用于创建与更新 ``.po`` 文件"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:15 356cfce9e6c84ffe8af39eedacb384ff
msgid "a Chinese build driven by ``DOCS_LANGUAGE=zh_CN``"
msgstr "由 ``DOCS_LANGUAGE=zh_CN`` 驱动的中文构建"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:17 87baacec168748ebae0a4a145e5f9867
msgid ""
"This avoids maintaining a separate ``docs/zh/`` tree and keeps page "
"structure aligned with the English site."
msgstr "这样无需单独维护 ``docs/zh/`` 目录树，页面结构可与英文站点保持一致。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:21 369aa156d7294991a5193b87979e85c2
msgid "Local Commands"
msgstr "本地命令"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:23 4fd221580e8d4600af6cc31146164c7e
msgid "Run these commands from the repository root:"
msgstr "在仓库根目录执行以下命令："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:33 f0881e89934b4fec826ce9775b15b9d7
msgid "Command reference:"
msgstr "命令说明："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:39 a2da2590d287401abd13afff931aa72c
msgid "Command"
msgstr "命令"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:40 160430385bdb47388c49ca4083391e88
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "用途"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:41 ded556161583486d8e32eb196696ff82
msgid "``make docs-gettext``"
msgstr "``make docs-gettext``"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:42 3f695d4ab6d74265832c9aa777c4558e
msgid "Generate gettext ``.pot`` catalogs under ``docs/_build/gettext/``"
msgstr "在 ``docs/_build/gettext/`` 下生成 gettext ``.pot`` 目录"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:43 260ea94a7bc64dc69784c6985467d296
msgid "``make docs-i18n-init``"
msgstr "``make docs-i18n-init``"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:44 13afece57b1d45a0ace183345f1298c8
msgid "Initialize or update ``zh_CN`` translation files in ``docs/locale/``"
msgstr "在 ``docs/locale/`` 中初始化或更新 `` zh_CN`` 翻译文件"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:45 4db71b66501c41f9918c1aa175983da6
msgid "``make docs-i18n-update``"
msgstr "``make docs-i18n-update``"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:46 8500d1a73933428a84cd6e6eb1ba878b
msgid "Refresh existing ``zh_CN`` translation files after English source changes"
msgstr "在英文源变更后刷新已有的 ``zh_CN`` 翻译文件"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:47 59c8da1083464164985b5609b9c9dd4d
msgid "``make docs-zh``"
msgstr "``make docs-zh``"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:48 a564ac3654c34b02af171d812526e242
msgid "Build the Chinese HTML site into ``docs/_build/html/zh_CN/``"
msgstr "将中文 HTML 站点构建到 ``docs/_build/html/zh_CN/``"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:49 32f7af8cf7c046a282383a2dc9aa0877
msgid "``make docs-zh-strict``"
msgstr "``make docs-zh-strict``"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:50 024a99eec5124fcdbbb4bdb9c9ed1355
msgid "Build the Chinese HTML site with warnings treated as errors"
msgstr "构建中文 HTML 站点，并将警告视为错误"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:53 ceaf2f7c235e4249ad5753d25a030627
msgid "Translation Workflow"
msgstr "翻译流程"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:55 3261df8d94b0489c82d51bf6f74d450a
msgid "When the English documentation changes:"
msgstr "当英文文档发生变更时："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:57 4236b922a7194f218a5be03ee1a05b09
msgid "Edit the English source files under ``docs/``."
msgstr "编辑 ``docs/`` 下的英文源文件。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:58 090e3ff79a624f6fa06c3a977548f90b
msgid "Regenerate gettext catalogs:"
msgstr "重新生成 gettext 目录："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:64 7e4694880f9a42bd9f34311a7b1faf8d
msgid "Update the Chinese translation files:"
msgstr "更新中文翻译文件："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:70 f679438a0d6f44298dd2dc4a39cca162
msgid ""
"Translate the new or modified strings in "
"``docs/locale/zh_CN/LC_MESSAGES/*.po``."
msgstr "翻译 ``docs/locale/zh_CN/LC_MESSAGES/*.po`` 中新增或修改的字符串。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:71 ec4e76055d50496bbf20922d570b35e5
msgid "Build the Chinese site locally:"
msgstr "在本地构建中文站点："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:77 cb8ab0c761e4455a9417c4a21596891c
msgid "If you need stricter validation, run:"
msgstr "若需要更严格的校验，请执行："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:85 6df5b146cf7d4ac3b66a50e1b84279fd
msgid ""
"``gettext_uuid = True`` is enabled in ``docs/conf.py`` to reduce churn in "
"``.po`` files when source paragraphs are moved around."
msgstr ""
"已在 ``docs/conf.py`` 中启用 `` gettext_uuid = True``，以便在源段落调整位置时减少 ``.po`` "
"文件的无关变动。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:89 6fedb245c3634f498b43347a3ba1ce1f
msgid "Read the Docs Setup"
msgstr "Read the Docs 配置"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:91 34316f7f3812403e820e7630b14a43fb
msgid "Use two Read the Docs projects that point to the same repository:"
msgstr "使用两个指向同一仓库的 Read the Docs 项目："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:93 fc7a342fb0db4184b51a1e8ed6087920
msgid "**English parent project**"
msgstr "**英文父项目**"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:95 f26f6eb001a842e8a86e6b01c04b066c
msgid "Keep the existing English project as the parent project."
msgstr "将现有英文项目保留为父项目。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:96 ae6008cdb17744079e240eb50d38ebd6
msgid "Set its language to ``English`` in the RTD project settings."
msgstr "在 RTD 项目设置中将其语言设为 ``English``。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:98 2c1ff7cddfb34df6a367fb576e3c9e1e
msgid "**Chinese translation project**"
msgstr "**中文翻译项目**"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:100 e4a62f6d922346a0b9b50b4c4e9fd8a8
msgid "Create a second RTD project from the same repository."
msgstr "基于同一仓库再创建一个 RTD 项目。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:101 186c868f9722430585a4f984c69faa6e
msgid "Set its language to ``Chinese (Simplified)``."
msgstr "将其语言设为 ``Chinese (Simplified)``。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:102 6dd4ab4be0da49998eae3f5d1cab64b0
msgid "Attach it to the English project under ``Translations``."
msgstr "在 ``Translations`` 下将其关联到英文项目。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:104 0575b51ce5954670bca73ea7f666b7b2
msgid ""
"With this setup, Read the Docs will expose both languages under the same "
"site and provide the language switcher automatically."
msgstr "这样配置后，Read the Docs 会在同一站点下提供两种语言，并自动提供语言切换器。"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:108 69d489ad16bf443eb3e3a0ec9bf2f42a
msgid "How language selection works"
msgstr "语言切换是如何工作的"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:110 647443e68c5249348725f13399aac158
msgid ""
"``docs/conf.py`` resolves the build language from ``DOCS_LANGUAGE`` first "
"and falls back to ``READTHEDOCS_LANGUAGE``. This keeps local builds and RTD "
"builds on the same configuration path:"
msgstr ""
"``docs/conf.py`` 优先从 `` DOCS_LANGUAGE`` 解析构建语言，其次回退到 `` "
"READTHEDOCS_LANGUAGE``，从而使本地构建与 RTD 构建走同一套配置："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:114 0874efb10fcb48d2a047cdc033de296d
msgid "local Chinese build: ``DOCS_LANGUAGE=zh_CN``"
msgstr "本地中文构建：``DOCS_LANGUAGE=zh_CN``"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:115 9c74e055f22d4b52af5d2ff023f8fdfc
msgid "RTD Chinese project: ``READTHEDOCS_LANGUAGE=zh-cn`` (provided by RTD)"
msgstr "RTD 中文项目：``READTHEDOCS_LANGUAGE=zh-cn`` （由 RTD 提供）"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:118 bb2567c3a37744d9a050d24bd9720cea
msgid "Scope of the first Chinese rollout"
msgstr "首批中文化范围"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:120 e01f10ca6764437f8b2305bca3058a56
msgid ""
"The current setup scaffolds ``.po`` files for all pages already linked from "
"the site navigation, including:"
msgstr "当前配置已为站点导航中已链接的所有页面生成 ``.po`` 文件骨架，包括："

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:123 811d31c8f2794ecdb39e9a500d6cd9ae
msgid ""
"``index``, ``quickstart``, ``installation``, ``usage_guide``, ``cookbook``, "
"``faq``"
msgstr ""
"``index``、`` quickstart``、`` installation``、`` usage_guide``、`` "
"cookbook``、`` faq``"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:124 95992ac17dbd456fb703194da490729e
msgid "all pages under ``models/``"
msgstr "``models/`` 下的所有页面"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:125 5c93bc87687747deacc5f88364dfa0e8
msgid "all pages under ``finetuning/``"
msgstr "``finetuning/`` 下的所有页面"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:126 298bfbd4e3934542824b106ee63e453a
msgid "all pages under ``reference/``"
msgstr "``reference/`` 下的所有页面"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:127 0399fcec202b4ae2ad37d1eb024fb1ef
msgid "all pages under ``deployment/`` and ``integrations/``"
msgstr "``deployment/`` 与 `` integrations/`` 下的所有页面"

#: ../../reference/translations.rst:129 04e4b7c78b154614b0445decbeb23e73
msgid ""
"This means the infrastructure is ready for a phased translation rollout "
"without changing the site structure again later."
msgstr "这意味着基础设施已就绪，可分阶段推进翻译，而无需日后再次调整站点结构。"

